Package: phil.concepts.db
Title: Philosophical Concept Annotation Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yusuke", "Matsui", email = "mail.to.matsui@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: AnnotationDbi-style database for philosophical concepts.
    Provides concept IDs, multilingual labels, definitions, tradition
    associations, and cross-references to Wikidata and InPhO.
